{"tid":2213256,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版國安法｜16英國議員去信外相要求會面 促向BNO港人提供法律協助和難民庇護","createTime":"2020-09-22T11:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T13:30:24.000Z","uid":70063,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41109aa498778b3d5877be347c87c218dfff5bc3","tid":2213256,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1307943793363161088?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1307943793363161088%3Fs%3D19&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2xkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=9abe8b10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fipacglobal%2Fstatus%2F1307943793363161088%3Fs%3D19&h=d5c12e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ipacglobal/status/1307943793363161088?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n16位英國議員聯署去信英國外相藍韜文，要求就多位持BNO的港人提供協助，並要求與藍韜文會面。聯署信指，隨著多位持BNO的港人被政治檢控，而英國對港有清晰和道德責任，英國不能對此坐視不理。<br />\n<br />\n他們要求英國政府，向所有在「港版國安法」下被拘捕的持BNO港人，提供全面的法律和領事服務，及在有需要時向他們提供難民庇護。他們批評駐港英國總領事館，拒絕向被「港版國安法」迫害的港人提供難民庇護，對此感到憂慮和十分不安。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信包括16位來自對華政策跨國議會聯盟（IPAC）的國會議員，包括David Alton、Chris Bryant、Natalie Bennett、Alistair Carmichael、Judith Cummins、David Davis等。<br />\n<br />\n他們指，自「港版國安法」通過後，港人的自由和權利被侵蝕，司法獨立遭削弱，被「港版國安法」控告的人未必能享有公平審訊，甚至乎可被引渡回內地受審，刑罰可高達終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n流亡英國的前眾志主席羅冠聰在Facebook指，在中英聯合聲明中，中方曾聲明BNO持有人在中國境內（包括香港）不可享有英國的領事保護，相信英國政府亦未必會接納這些議員的建議。若英國在此時決定向BNO持有人提供相關支援，相信中方會有強烈反彈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/LKVFJVXOFNDZDL4OUWROXUIGGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FLKVFJVXOFNDZDL4OUWROXUIGGM%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2xkIbV9%2FoY%2BmeTBoP0X2IjM%3D&h=11e462d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FLKVFJVXOFNDZDL4OUWROXUIGGM%2F&h=90f57943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/LKVFJVXOFNDZDL4OUWROXUIGGM/</a>"},{"pid":"e1a9c295ea3e99503ae7231077f99512a4b1b289","tid":2213256,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27a7766bd3694362bd82ef42317916269dda405","tid":2213256,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5df01bbe279310ab244ff8f8b5d978bc3487d85","tid":2213256,"uid":18210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:40:30.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c98a59e9f5333f7874898871306aac41506b84fb","tid":2213256,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56dcd4e84fa9c651763d5453740afd0d9c6ca9a5","tid":2213256,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7185099e6da257725587afa33c19174b2dc6b36d","tid":2213256,"uid":264326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0a50663a0f6478d241f705c01c44ff47761d00","tid":2213256,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T11:59:05.000Z","msg":"無BNO已成condom。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03567207ff56b8a3e251e45b94ce349431e3c94","tid":2213256,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco